\\\"line\\\">2<\\/span> <span class=\\\"line\\\">3<\\/span> <span class=\\\"line\\\">4<\\/span> <span class=\\\"line\\\">5<\\/span> <span class=\\\"line\\\">6<\\/span> <span class=\\\"line\\\">7<\\/span> <span class=\\\"line\\\">8<\\/span> <span class=\\\"line\\\">9<\\/span> <span class=\\\"line\\\">10<\\/span> <span class=\\\"line\\\">11<\\/span> <\\/pre>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/td>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<td class=\\\"code\\\" style=\\\"vertical-align:middle;border:none;\\\">\\n<pre><span class=\\\"line\\\">\\/\\/ 默认 对应SQL: WHERE `name` LIKE \'%username%\'<\\/span> <span class=\\\"line\\\">[\'like\', \'name\', \'username\'] <\\/span> <span class=\\\"line\\\"><\\/span> <span class=\\\"line\\\">\\/**<\\/span> <span class=\\\"line\\\"> * 第二个范围值是一个数组，那么将会生成用 AND 串联起来的 多个 like 语句<\\/span> <span class=\\\"line\\\"> * 对应SQL: WHERE `name` LIKE \'%user%\' AND `name` LIKE \'%name%\'<\\/span> <span class=\\\"line\\\"> *\\/<\\/span> <span class=\\\"line\\\">[\'like\', \'name\', [\'user\', \'name\']]<\\/span> <span class=\\\"line\\\"><\\/span> <span class=\\\"line\\\">\\/\\/ 使用前缀查询 对应SQL: WHERE `name` LIKE \'user%\'<\\/span> <span class=\\\"line\\\">[\'like\', \'name\', \'user%\', false]<\\/span> <\\/pre>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/td>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/tr>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/tbody>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/table>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t<li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tor like 与like 相同,只是第二个范围值是一个数组，那么将会生成用 OR 串联起来的 多个 like 语句\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"table-container\\\" style=\\\"margin:0px;\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<table style=\\\"width:auto;font-size:14px;margin:0px;border:none;\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<tbody>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<tr>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<td class=\\\"gutter\\\" style=\\\"vertical-align:middle;border:none;\\\">\\n<pre><span class=\\\"line\\\">1<\\/span> <span class=\\\"line\\\">2<\\/span> <span class=\\\"line\\\">3<\\/span> <span class=\\\"line\\\">4<\\/span> <span c